title: The Shawshank Redemption (1994)
description: A man is sentenced to life in prison for a crime he didn't commit, and befriends a fellow inmate while trying to prove his innocence.

title: The Godfather (1972)
description: The head of a powerful mafia family tries to pass on his legacy to his reluctant son, amidst a world of crime and violence.

title: The Dark Knight (2008)
description: Batman must confront his greatest enemy, the Joker, who is wreaking havoc on the city of Gotham.

title: Forrest Gump (1994)
description: A simple man with a low IQ goes on a journey through life, meeting historical figures and experiencing key moments in American history.

title: Star Wars: Episode IV
description: A New Hope (1977) - A young farm boy joins a rebellion against an evil empire and becomes a hero in a galaxy far, far away.

title: The Silence of the Lambs (1991)
description: A young FBI agent seeks the help of a cannibalistic serial killer in order to catch another serial killer who is on the loose.

title: Pulp Fiction (1994)
description: The lives of several characters intertwine in this nonlinear tale of crime, violence, and redemption.

title: The Matrix (1999)
description: A hacker discovers that the world he lives in is a simulated reality created by machines, and joins a rebellion against them.

title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring (2001)
description: A young hobbit is tasked with destroying a powerful ring that could destroy the world, and forms a fellowship to help him.

title: Inception (2010)
description: A skilled thief enters people's dreams in order to steal their secrets, but is hired to implant an idea instead.
